  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span dir=\"ltr\">Category:</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">Clan</span><span id=\"page381R_mcid37\" class=\"markedContent\"><br /></span><span dir=\"ltr\">Prerequisite:</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">Jiton Clan, Level 8+</span></p><p><span id=\"page381R_mcid38\" class=\"markedContent\">You have learned to imbue deadly poison within your jutsu. You gain the following benefits</span></p><p>• Increase your Constitution or Intelligence score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p><p>• When you use your Magnet Release feature to change the damage type of a jutsu with the Wind or Earth Release keywords to Earth, you can change it to poison instead</p><p>• Once per turn, when you deal poison damage, you can force the target to make a Constitution saving throw vs your Ninjutsu Save DC, becoming poisoned for 1 minute on a failed save. You can use this feature a number of times equal to your Ninjutsu ability modifier per long rest.</p>",
